    "summary": {
      "value": "Increase the potency of Drain spells."
    },
    "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Entropist </strong>and <strong>Necromancer</strong>, and must have learned both the <strong>Drain Spirit</strong> and <strong>Drain Vigor</strong> spells.</p><hr /><p>When you cast the <strong>Drain Spirit</strong> or <strong>Drain Vigor</strong> spells, the amount of Mind Points or Hit Points you recover is <strong>equal</strong> to the MP or HP loss suffered by the target, respectively (instead of being halved).</p><p>Additionally, the amount of Mind Point loss caused by <strong>Drain Spirit</strong> spells you cast is increased by 5 if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, or by 10 if you are <strong>level 40 or higher</strong>.</p>",
